'''柏保路·科奴斯'''（{{lang-es|Pablo Fornals}}，{{IPA-es|ˈpaβlo foɾˈnals}}；{{bd|1996年|12月22日}}）是一名[[西班牙|西班牙]]職業足球員，主踢[[進攻中場|進攻中場]]位置，效力於英超球隊[[韋斯咸足球俱樂部|韋斯咸]]。

在[[西班牙甲組足球聯賽|西甲]]的四個賽季，他為[[馬拉加足球會|馬拉加]]和[[維拉利爾足球會|維拉利爾]]一共上陣129場比賽和射入12個入球。2019年，他簽約轉會至英超球隊[[韋斯咸足球俱樂部|韋斯咸]]。科奴斯於2016年開始他在西甲以正選球員上陣。

==球員生涯==
===馬拉加===
科奴斯出生於[[華倫西亞自治區|華倫西亞自治區]]的[[卡斯特利翁-德拉普拉納|卡斯特利翁]]，於2012年以16歲加入馬拉加的青年軍<ref>{{cite news|url=http://malagacf.diariosur.es/noticias/201503/25/sellada-renovacion-pablo-corto-20150324231541.html|title=Sellada la renovación de Pablo, a corto plazo en la órbita del primer equipo|trans-title=Sealed the renewal of Pablo, short-time target for the first team|newspaper=Diario Sur|first=Sergio|last=Cortés|language=es|date=25 March 2015|accessdate=26 September 2015|archive-date=2019-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190810171654/https://malagacf.diariosur.es/noticias/201503/25/sellada-renovacion-pablo-corto-20150324231541.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在2014-15賽季[[西班牙丙組足球聯賽|西丙]]的預備隊中首次上陣。

科奴斯於2015年9月26日在西甲為一隊上陣的首場比賽，當時與[[皇家馬德里|皇家馬德里]]比賽，並以0-0打和<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.marca.com/eventos/marcador/futbol/2015_16/la-liga/jornada_6/rma_mga/|title=Kameni para al Madrid|trans-title=Kameni stops Madrid|newspaper=[[Marca_(newspaper)|Marca]]|first=Santiago|last=Siguero|language=es|date=26 September 2015|accessdate=26 September 2015|archive-date=2019-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190416135817/https://www.marca.com/eventos/marcador/futbol/2015_16/la-liga/jornada_6/rma_mga/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩個月零兩天後，他在[[玫瑰園球場|玫瑰園球場]]與[[安達盧西亞|安達盧西亞]]的鄰隊[[格蘭納達足球會|格蘭納達]]進行比賽，在打和2-2的比賽中在入替[[杜達|杜達]]四分鐘後射入首個頂級聯賽入球<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.marca.com/2015/11/29/futbol/equipos/malaga/1448753133.html|title=Fornals, la última perla del Málaga|trans-title=Fornals, Málaga's latest gem|newspaper=Marca|language=es|date=29 November 2015|accessdate=24 February 2016|archive-date=2019-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190810161654/https://www.marca.com/2015/11/29/futbol/equipos/malaga/1448753133.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年12月4日，科奴斯在維拉利爾以2–2的比賽中再次入球<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.marca.com/eventos/marcador/futbol/2016_17/la-liga/jornada_14/val_mga/|title=Fornals borra la sonrisa de Prandelli|trans-title=Fornals wipes Prandelli's smile|newspaper=Marca|first=Pablo|last=Egea|language=es|date=4 December 2016|accessdate=4 December 2016|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101110020/https://www.marca.com/eventos/marcador/futbol/2016_17/la-liga/jornada_14/val_mga/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===維拉利爾===
2017年7月24日，以前身為青年軍效力的球隊維拉利爾在支付1200萬歐元的買斷條款價格後簽入科奴斯<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.villarrealcf.es/noticias/indice-general/noticias-generales/item/18258-pablo-fornals-regresa-al-villarreal-cf|title=Pablo Fornals regresa al Villarreal CF|trans-title=Pablo Fornals returns to Villarreal CF|publisher=Villarreal CF|language=es|date=24 July 2017|accessdate=24 July 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805055909/http://www.villarrealcf.es/noticias/indice-general/noticias-generales/item/18258-pablo-fornals-regresa-al-villarreal-cf|archive-date=5 August 2017}}</ref>，為期5年，科奴斯因而離開馬拉加<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11844/10960093/pablo-fornals-pays-own-release-clause-to-join-villarreal-from-malaga|title=Pablo Fornals pays own release clause to join Villarreal from Malaga|publisher=[[Sky_Sports|Sky Sports]]|date=24 July 2017|accessdate=14 June 2019|archive-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620121031/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11844/10960093/pablo-fornals-pays-own-release-clause-to-join-villarreal-from-malaga|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後的1月13日，他在一次反攻的機會下以一個遲來的笠射為新球會射入首個入球，使他的新球隊於[[聖地牙哥·班拿貝球場|聖地牙哥·班拿貝球場]]以1-0首次擊敗[[皇家馬德里|皇家馬德里]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.marca.com/en/football/real-madrid/2018/01/13/5a5a412a268e3eee628b4603.html|title=Fornals produces wonderful moment to secure a historic victory at the Bernabeu|newspaper=Marca|date=13 January 2018|accessdate=15 January 2018|archive-date=2018-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181009130935/http://www.marca.com/en/football/real-madrid/2018/01/13/5a5a412a268e3eee628b4603.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年9月26日，科奴斯在對[[畢爾包體育會|畢爾包]]的作客以一記50碼中距離窩利抽射在聯賽中射入是季首個入球，最終以3-0獲勝<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadspin.com/pablo-fornals-might-have-just-scored-the-goal-of-the-se-1829343457|title=Pablo Fornals might have just scored the goal of the season|publisher=Deadspin|first=Billy|last=Haisley|date=26 September 2018|accessdate=10 October 2018|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117125110/https://deadspin.com/pablo-fornals-might-have-just-scored-the-goal-of-the-se-1829343457|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://eu.usatoday.com/story/sports/soccer/2018/09/27/spain-discovers-next-midfield-talent-in-pablo-fornals/37956603/|title=Spain discovers next midfield talent in Pablo Fornals|newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=27 September 2018|accessdate=10 October 2018|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109041604/https://eu.usatoday.com/story/sports/soccer/2018/09/27/spain-discovers-next-midfield-talent-in-pablo-fornals/37956603/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===韋斯咸===
2019年6月14日，科奴斯與韋斯咸簽下一份為期五年的合約，據稱轉會費為2400萬英鎊，這使他成為該英超球會第二高轉會費的簽入球員<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48636017|title=Pablo Fornals: West Ham sign Spain forward for £24m|publisher=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|date=14 June 2019|accessdate=14 June 2019|archive-date=2019-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812085211/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48636017|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.whufc.com/news/articles/2019/june/14-june/fornals-why-moving-west-ham-was-easiest-decision|title=Fornals: Why moving to West Ham was the easiest decision|publisher=West Ham United F.C.|date=14 June 2019|accessdate=15 June 2019|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810214533/https://www.whufc.com/news/articles/2019/june/14-june/fornals-why-moving-west-ham-was-easiest-decision|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他於8月10日進行了英超聯賽首戰，在主場以0-5被曼城擊敗的比賽中，在半場時間入替[[米查爾·安東尼奧|米查爾·安東尼奧]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49215984|title=West Ham 0–5 Manchester City: Raheem Sterling gets hat-trick in VAR-dominated game|publisher=BBC Sport|first=Gary|last=Rose|date=10 August 2019|accessdate=10 August 2019|archive-date=2019-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191228004651/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49215984|dead-url=no}}</ref>。科奴斯在8月27日在[[英格蘭足球聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]第二輪比賽中為新球隊射入自己的首球，以2比0戰勝[[紐波特郡足球俱樂部|紐波特郡]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49403011|title=Carabao Cup: Newport County 0–2 West Ham United|publisher=BBC Sport|first=Dafydd|last=Pritchard|date=27 August 2019|accessdate=27 August 2019|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107230740/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49403011|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年5月23日，[[英超|英超]]联赛第38轮西漢姆主场對上[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|南安普敦]]3-0勝利，福納斯首发出场，梅開二度連進兩球，是球隊前進[[欧足联欧洲联赛|欧足联欧洲联赛]]的功臣之一。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://soccer.nbcsports.com/2021/05/23/west-ham-southampton-video-highlights-reaction-analysis-recap/|title=West Ham seal Europa League qualification|publisher=NBC Sports|date=2021-05-23|access-date=2021-05-23|archive-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523210608/https://soccer.nbcsports.com/2021/05/23/west-ham-southampton-video-highlights-reaction-analysis-recap/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==國際賽生涯==
2016年3月28日，科奴斯首次代表[[西班牙21歲以下國家足球隊|西班牙U21]]在[[新孔多米納球場|新孔多米納球場]]上的比賽中打足90分鐘以1-0擊敗挪威<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.laopiniondemalaga.es/malagacf/2016/03/29/pablo-fornals-debuta-sub21-gusta/838735.html|title=Pablo Fornals debuta con la sub´21 y se gusta|trans-title=Pablo Fornals debuts with the under-21 and impresses|newspaper=La Opinión de Málaga|first=José|last=Criado|language=es|date=29 March 2016|accessdate=29 May 2016|archive-date=2018-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180908092810/https://www.laopiniondemalaga.es/malagacf/2016/03/29/pablo-fornals-debuta-sub21-gusta/838735.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月17日，[[維辛迪·迪保斯基|維辛迪·迪保斯基]]徵召他入國家隊與波斯尼亞和黑塞哥維那進行一場友誼賽<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.malagacf.com/en/news/pablo-called-up-to-join-spains-first-team|title=Pablo called-up to join Spain’s first team|publisher=Málaga CF|date=17 May 2016|accessdate=29 May 2016|archive-date=2018-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180908092747/https://www.malagacf.com/en/news/pablo-called-up-to-join-spains-first-team|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他在12天後在[[瑞士|瑞士]][[聖加侖|聖加侖]]的[[康步公園|AFG競技場]]首次上陣入替[[米基·聖荷西|米基·聖荷西]]，最終以3比1獲勝<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.marca.com/eventos/marcador/futbol/2015_16/amistosos_seleccion/3/spa_bih/|title=Nolito endulza un duelo atípico|trans-title=Nolito sweetens an atypical duel|newspaper=Marca|first=Tomás|last=Campos|language=es|date=29 May 2016|accessdate=29 May 2016|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403190413/https://www.marca.com/eventos/marcador/futbol/2015_16/amistosos_seleccion/3/spa_bih/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

同年6月，科奴斯為西班牙U21隊贏得[[2019年U21歐洲國家盃|2019年U21歐洲國家盃]]<ref name=U21>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48812993|title=Spain U21 2–1 Germany U21|publisher=BBC Sport|first=Emlyn|last=Begley|date=30 June 2019|accessdate=1 July 2019|archive-date=2019-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190704001636/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48812993|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[意大利|意大利]]和[[聖馬力諾|聖馬力諾]]舉行的比賽中，他在對比利時（2-1）<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.marca.com/futbol/seleccion/cronica/2019/06/19/5d0a6cc3ca4741695c8b4612.html|title=Fornals mantiene en pie a España|trans-title=Fornals keeps Spain standing|newspaper=Marca|first=Miguel Ángel|last=García|language=es|date=19 June 2019|accessdate=16 September 2019|archive-date=2019-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190627012118/https://www.marca.com/futbol/seleccion/cronica/2019/06/19/5d0a6cc3ca4741695c8b4612.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和波蘭（5-0）<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.mundodeportivo.com/seleccion-espanola/20190622/463050990712/sub-21-espana-europeo-italia-polonia.html|title=5–0: Manita de oro de La Rojita|trans-title=5–0: Golden fiver by ''La Rojita''|newspaper=[[Mundo_Deportivo|Mundo Deportivo]]|first=Óscar|last=Zárate|language=es|date=22 June 2019|accessdate=16 September 2019|archive-date=2019-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190624180917/https://www.mundodeportivo.com/seleccion-espanola/20190622/463050990712/sub-21-espana-europeo-italia-polonia.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>的兩場小組賽中取得入球。

